"<p align=\"center\" style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:18pt; font-weight:600; color:#00007f;\">Measurement of DC Currents, Voltage, Resistances, and study of Resistance color code</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt; color:#00007f;\"> </span></p>\n"
