"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:18pt;\">To study the use of multimeter in measurement of current, voltage and resistance.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
