"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:18pt;\">1.1</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt;\">         </span><span style=\" font-size:18pt;\">For the circuit of figure-10, find the current in each element and he voltage across         each element. Show the Kirchhoff’s laws are satisfied.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
